#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Küsimused ja vastused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I start &konversation;, I'd like to connect to a server without joining "
"any channels. How do I do that?"
msgstr ""
"Tahaksin &konversation;i käivitades kohe ühenduda serveriga, aga mitte mõne "
"konkreetse kanaliga. Kuidas seda teha?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Edit Server</link> screen, "
"leave the <guilabel>Channels</guilabel> frame empty."
msgstr ""
"Jäta dialoogis <link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Serveri "
"redigeerimine</link> sektsioon <guilabel>Kanalid</guilabel> puutumata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; won't connect to any servers. What is wrong?"
msgstr "&konversation; ei saa ühegi serveriga ühendust. Milles asi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3212
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are several things that could be wrong."
msgstr "Sellel võib olla mitu põhjust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that you have entered the correct <guilabel>Server name</guilabel> "
"and the correct <guilabel>Port</guilabel> in the <link linkend=\"serverlist-"
"addserver\">Add Server</link> screen."
msgstr ""
"Kontrolli, et <guilabel>serveri nimi</guilabel> ja <guilabel>port</guilabel> "
"on dialoogis <link linkend=\"serverlist-addserver\">Serveri lisamine</link> "
"korrektselt sisestatud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the output in the <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Server "
"Messages</link> screen for any error messages. Did the server reject the "
"connection because of a bad password? Did the server reject the connection "
"because it requires <acronym>IDENTD</acronym> and your computer did not "
"respond to the <acronym>IDENT</acronym> request? Did you check the SSL "
"protocol box but the server does not support SSL?"
msgstr ""
"Kontrolli kaardi <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Serveri sõnumid</"
"link> teateid. Kas seal on teateid mingitest vigadest? Kas server keeldus "
"ühendusest vigase parooli tõttu? Kas server keeldus seepärast, et talle on "
"vajalik <acronym>IDENTD</acronym>, aga sinu arvuti serveri <acronym>IDENTD</"
"acronym> soovile ei vastanud? Kas oled märkinud SSL protokolli kasutamist "
"lubava kasti, aga server ei toeta SSL-i?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are behind a firewall, make sure the correct ports are enabled. "
"&konversation; needs the following ports enabled:"
msgstr ""
"Kui oled tulemüüri taga, kontrolli, et korrektsed pordid oleks ikka lubatud. "
"&konversation; vajab tööks järgmisi porte:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outgoing TCP 6667 (or the port of the server you connect to)"
msgstr ""
"Väljapoole TCP 6667 (või selle serveri port, millega ühendust soovid võtta)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incoming TCP 113 (if the server requires IDENTD)"
msgstr "Sissepoole TCP 113 (kui serverile on vajalik IDENTD)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3239
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For more information on &irc; connection problems, see <ulink url="
#| "\"http://www.irchelp.org/irchelp/networks/connectprob.html\">irchelp.org</"
#| "ulink>."
msgid ""
"For more information on &irc; connection problems, see <ulink url=\"https://"
"github.com/irchelp/wio/blob/gh-pages/networks/connectprob.md\">irchelp.org</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Rohkem infot &irc; ühenduse probleemide kohta annab <ulink url=\"http://www."
"irchelp.org/irchelp/networks/connectprob.html\">irchelp.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I go to <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel "
"List</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>, I cannot select it. Why is that?"
msgstr ""
"Kui ma püüan valida käsku <menuchoice> <guimenu>Aken</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Kanalite nimekiri</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>, ei saa ma seda "
"teha. Miks?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3257
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel List</"
#| "guisubmenu> </menuchoice> menu entry will be grayed-out if a non-channel "
#| "tab, &eg; <guilabel>Watched Nicks Online</guilabel>, is currently being "
#| "viewed. To make it selectable again go back to a channel tab or the "
#| "server tab."
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel List</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> menu entry will be grayed-out if a non-channel "
"tab, &eg; <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel>, is currently being viewed. To "
"make it selectable again go back to a channel tab or the server tab."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Aken</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Kanalite nimekiri</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> on hall ja mittekasutatav, kui parajasti on avatud "
"mingi kanaliväline kaart, näiteks <guilabel>Jälgitavad hüüdnimed võrgus</"
"guilabel>. Et seda käsku valida, muuda aktiivseks mõne kanali või serveri "
"kaart."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I have &konversation; automatically mark me as away after a period of "
"inactivity?"
msgstr ""
"Kuidas panna &konversation; automaatselt märkima mind eemalolevaks pärast "
"teatavat mitteaktiivsuse perioodi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Auto-away messages are configured on a per-identity basis. To enable auto-"
"away select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Identities</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Choose the identity for which you want to enable "
"auto-away from the drop down list at the top of the dialog and go to the "
"<guilabel>Away</guilabel> tab. Check the <guilabel>Automatic Away</guilabel> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Automaatse eemaloleku sõnumeid saab seadistada igale identiteedile eraldi. "
"Selleks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Identiteedid</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vali dialoogi "
"ülaosas asuvast rippmenüüst identiteet, mille puhul soovid automaatse "
"eemalolekuteate sisse lülitada, ning vali kaart <guilabel>Eemalolek</"
"guilabel>. Märgi ära valik <guilabel>Automaatne eemalolek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How to avoid the <guilabel>Auto Replace</guilabel> feature of the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface>?"
msgstr ""
"Kuidas vältida <interface>sisestusreal</interface> <guilabel>automaatse "
"asendamise</guilabel> võimalust?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> instead of just "
"&Enter; to avoid parsing and automatically replacing the text in the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface> according to the options in the settings "
"dialog page <menuchoice><guimenu>Behavior</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Auto "
"Replace</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Kasuta kiirklahvi <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> "
"lihtsalt &Enter;i asemel, et vältida <interface>sisestusrea</interface> "
"teksti parsimist ja automaatset asendamist vastavalt sellele, kuidas see on "
"määratud seadistustedialoogis <menuchoice><guimenu>Käitumine</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Automaatne asendamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

